$interpreted: Sophie: Oh, no! He's getting back up! If this keeps happening there's no way we'll win!
Angelia: Colonel Dylan, Headmaster Charle, do you have a way?
Dylan: Sorry, your Highness, my abilites are lacking. Forgive me for disappointing you.
Charle: Me...too. There's nothing that I can think of...I'm sorry.
Hanbei: Hey Hey Hey! If all these guys got nothing, then we don't need to stay here, right?
Sharice: Y-You're r-r-r-right. I ain't a-a-a-afraid.
Sharice: It is not b-b-b-because I'm afraid. I'm just p-p-p-protecting you all.
Uzziah: ——I'd advise you to back off a bit. That would be best.
Naya: What the hell is this guy doing here!?
Charle: It's you...!
Sophie: Ah! That time in the Colosseum...
Sophie: Yeah, you were controlling the monsters...
Sophie: What do you know!? Tell us, now!
Uzziah: ...I'm afraid I don't know much more than you.
Uzziah: What lies before you...is no ordinary monster.
Uzziah: Rather, it is the Monster of Judgement that the Immortals used all their power to keep sealed away.
Sophie: Eh? Mon...Monster of Judgement...? What are you saying?
Uzziah: You don't need to understand, you just need to know that as it stands, there's no way you can defeat it.
Angelia: How...
Uzziah: The only way is to seal the Monster of Judgement back underneath the Dragon Tooth.
Sione: ...Just like the Dragoneye Gem of Atlas...
Clark: If that's the case, so long as we put the tooth back in place, we can block the monsters from coming out?
Misa: Then what are you staring at!? Get the Rib of the Snake God back in its place!
Uzziah: ...No. There is a key difference.
Angelia: Eh?
Uzziah: At that time, the King of the Kingdom of the Sun, who was your ancestor, he took the Dragoneye Gem to be a precious stone.
Uzziah: All who performed research on the Dragoneye Gem were extremely cautious and dared not damage it in the slightest.
Uzziah: ...But it looks like the Dragon Tooth has already been tampered with.
Uzziah: In order to create the wind barrier, Devious used the power of the Dragon Tooth and took it upon himself to change the Rune that's inscribed upon it.
Misa: So what are we going to do? If the void doesn't close, then the Desert Kingdom will——
Naya: Hey! Get away! It's about to erupt! Don't make a move until we've found a way!
Uzziah: We can reactivate the seal, but we'll need someone's help. We'll need to close it from the inside.
Dylan: The inside? You mean someone will have to sacrifice themself?
Sophie: What!? No way!
Rune: Sophie's right. We can't allow it!
Diana: ...I'm qualified for the task.
Misa: Your Majesty!
Diana: I'm the Queen of this Kingdom. If I can save it, no matter what the c——
: ﹝——Then I shall pay it, my child.﹞
Diana: Godfather!
Lazer: …………
Diana: Godfather! Come back! Godfather!
Rune: Now!
Uzziah: …………
Uzziah: Out of my way. Do not stop me.
Diana: God...Godfather...
Diana: You always do this to me...*sob*...why do you do this to...*sob*...me!?
Rune: ...Sophie says, "When you're down, you've got to laugh even harder".
Sophie: ...right.
Rune: So...is it okay to smile?
Sophie: Of course!
Rune: Well——
Sophie: ...But, for now...we ought to wait.
Sophie: Later...we will smile.
Sophie: For sure.
